name: Maruxa Murphy
what_you_do: Maruxa Murphy is an award-winning online community architect, having transformed 10,000 to 1 million-member communities across 20+ sectors.
who_you_serve: She believes in empowering all individuals to live their fullest lives, and her work has been instrumental in bringing people together to create positive change.
social_proof: She has been featured in Forbes, Reader's Digest, Fox News, The Huffington Post, NBC, and The Austin-American Statesman for her work in creating profitable enterprises that do good in the world. She was featured as one of 10 woman-owned to be featured at the United Nations on Women's Entrepreneur Day 2019 for her community-led coffee brand, Perky Perky.
signature_programs: The Power of Belonging and How To Revolutionize A New Generation of Business Growth, What It Takes To Create A Revolution
business_focus: Maruxa Murphy is an award-winning online community architect who transforms communities in person and online to become movements from 10,000 members to 1 Million members in over 20 different verticals primed to become leaders their industry.
